    <item>
      <title>特朗普对新鲜的胡塞威胁加大对伊朗的压力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-17/trump-ramps-up-pressure-on-iran-with-fresh-houthi-threats</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统对伊朗的压力施加了压力，要求他们遏制霍蒂斯（Houthis），如果也门的武装组织没有阻止其袭击，就提高了对伊斯兰共和国进行报复罢工的可能性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-17/trump-ramps-up-pressure-on-iran-with-fresh-houthi-threats</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Mar 2025 15:43:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟为基辅制定了400亿欧元的军事援助计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-17/eu-progressing-on-40-billion-military-aid-plan-for-kyiv</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟成员国朝着乌克兰的新军事援助方案取得了进展，价值高达400亿欧元（437亿美元），比本周晚些时候领导人的峰会提前几天。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-17/eu-progressing-on-40-billion-military-aid-plan-for-kyiv</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Mar 2025 15:39:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>主席说，FTC有资源可以接受大型技术。</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-17/ftc-has-the-resources-to-take-on-big-tech-chairman-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据机构主席安德鲁·弗格森（Andrew Ferguson）称，美国联邦贸易委员会正在为下个月的审判做准备，以打破Meta Platforms Inc.，并拥有向高管技术部门监管范围内的资源所需的资源。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-17/ftc-has-the-resources-to-take-on-big-tech-chairman-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Mar 2025 15:33:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
